description:
////// WELCOME //////
<p>Riftcast is a Windows application based on LCD virtual pets, designed to emulate the look and feel of a real electronic virtual pet, sorta. <br/></p>
<p> <strong>Be sure to check the readme for more information, mainly controls.</strong><br/></p>
////// FEATURES //////
<p>5* different eggs and over 12 obtainable monsters</p>
<p>No autosaving</p>
<p>Application skins<br/></p>
<p>And some other things</p>
////// COMING SOON //////
<p>Battling</p>
<p>Exploration<br/></p>
////// INFO //////
<p> This  application is currently in development and some features have yet to be implemented, but it's pretty much playable. Expect updates every now and then. <br/></p>
